          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Usage: coterm sidebar <validate|reload|select|open> [name|--all] [--json]\n\nValidate, reload, select, or open custom sidebars from ~/.config/coterm/sidebars.\nSwift files win over JSON files with the same base name.\n\nCommands:\n  validate [name]   Validate all custom sidebars, or one named sidebar\n  reload [name]     Validate all sidebars, then reload every valid one\n  select <name>     Validate and activate one custom sidebar\n  open <name>       Open one custom sidebar as a Bonsplit pane\n\nExamples:\n  coterm sidebar validate\n  coterm sidebar reload --all\n  coterm sidebar select finder.tree\n  coterm sidebar open finder.tree"
          }
        }
      }
    },
